title: TMJ challenges Annuar for FAM president post
text:
More 
Johor crown prince Tunku Ismail Ibrahim will be contesting for the post of Football Association of Malaysia president at the FAM's 53rd congress on March 25. 
This was announced by FAM secretary-general Hamidin Mohd Amin in a press conference at Wisma FAM, Kelana Jaya today.
